There aren‚Äôt a lot of wide open spaces and parks near me so, I was glad when I discovered this open field on the Wissahickon. This park is huge. It has three baseball fields and some soccer nets with wide open spaces to picnic and lounge. It has access to the Wissahickon trails and even has a map so you can plan your route.
